Package: canregtools
Title: Analyzing Population-Based Cancer Registry Data
Version: 0.2.9
Authors@R: 
    person("Qiong", "Chen", , "chenq08@126.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2401-0046",
           affiliation = "Department of Cancer Epidemiology, The Affiliated
           Cancer Hospital of Zhengzhou University & Henan Cancer Hospital,
           Henan Cancer Registry in China"))
Description: Tools for cleaning, analyzing, visualizing, and reporting data
    from Population-Based Cancer Registries (PBCRs), with standardized workflows
    for filtering, selecting, and restructuring data, designed for routine
    registry operations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/gigu003/canregtools,
